statements: SELECT * FROM WaterSystem;
SELECT system_name, system_id FROM WaterSystem ORDER BY system_id DESC;
SELECT system_name, oxygen_level FROM WaterSystem WHERE oxygen_level > 4.0;
SELECT system_id, system_name, filtration_process FROM WaterSystem WHERE filtration_process = 'Reverse Osmosis';
SELECT system_id, system_name FROM WaterSystem WHERE oxygen_level < 2.0 ORDER BY system_id ASC;
SELECT system_id, system_name, oxygen_level FROM WaterSystem ORDER BY system_id DESC;
SELECT system_name, filtration_process FROM WaterSystem WHERE oxygen_level > 5 ORDER BY system_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM WaterSystem WHERE filtration_process LIKE '%reverse%' ORDER BY oxygen_level DESC;
SELECT system_id, system_name, filtration_process, oxygen_level FROM WaterSystem WHERE filtration_process IN ('RO', 'UV') ORDER BY system_id ASC, oxygen_level DESC;
SELECT system_name, filtration_process, oxygen_level FROM WaterSystem ORDER BY oxygen_level ASC, system_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM aquaculture_tanks;
SELECT tank_id, tank_name, tank_type FROM aquaculture_tanks WHERE tank_type='Freshwater';
SELECT * FROM filtration_processes ORDER BY process_id DESC;
SELECT process_id, process_name FROM filtration_processes WHERE process_status='Active';
SELECT tank_id, tank_name, tank_type FROM aquaculture_tanks WHERE tank_capacity > 1000;
SELECT * FROM aquaculture_tanks WHERE tank_size > 100 AND water_type = 'freshwater' ORDER BY tank_id DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT tank_id, max_fish_capacity FROM aquaculture_tanks WHERE max_fish_capacity < 500 ORDER BY tank_id ASC
SELECT * FROM filtration_processes WHERE process_type = 'biofilter' AND start_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30' ORDER BY start_date DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT tank_id, water_type, max_fish_capacity FROM aquaculture_tanks WHERE max_fish_capacity > 1000 ORDER BY max_fish_capacity DESC
SELECT tank_id, water_type FROM aquaculture_tanks WHERE water_type IN ('freshwater', 'saltwater') ORDER BY tank_id ASC
SELECT * FROM WaterCirculationSystems;
SELECT system_name, pump_capacity FROM WaterCirculationSystems ORDER BY pump_capacity DESC;
SELECT process_name, filter_type FROM FiltrationProcesses WHERE filter_capacity > 100;
SELECT tank_id, oxygen_level, timestamp FROM OxygenLevels ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT system_id, system_name, pump_capacity, water_flow_rate FROM WaterCirculationSystems WHERE pump_capacity < 500;
SELECT system_id, system_name, pump_capacity FROM WaterCirculationSystems WHERE pump_capacity > 100 ORDER BY pump_capacity DESC
SELECT process_id, process_name, filter_type, filter_capacity FROM FiltrationProcesses WHERE filter_capacity < 50 ORDER BY process_id
SELECT tank_id, oxygen_level, timestamp FROM OxygenLevels WHERE oxygen_level > 5 ORDER BY timestamp DESC
SELECT system_name, pump_capacity, water_flow_rate FROM WaterCirculationSystems WHERE system_name LIKE '%A%' ORDER BY system_id
SELECT process_name, filter_type, filter_capacity FROM FiltrationProcesses WHERE filter_type IN ('carbon', 'sand') ORDER BY process_id
SELECT * FROM aquaculture_tanks;
SELECT tank_id, tank_size, water_volume FROM aquaculture_tanks WHERE water_quality = 'good';
SELECT * FROM filtration_processes ORDER BY filter_type DESC;
SELECT avg(oxygen_level) AS average_oxygen_level FROM oxygen_levels WHERE tank_id = 1;
SELECT tank_id, water_circulation_system_id FROM water_circulation_systems WHERE pump_power > 100;
SELECT * FROM aquaculture_tanks WHERE tank_size > 100 ORDER BY tank_id DESC
SELECT tank_id, tank_size, water_type FROM aquaculture_tanks WHERE water_type = 'Saltwater' AND tank_size BETWEEN 50 AND 200
SELECT * FROM filtration_processes WHERE process_type = 'Mechanical' OR process_type = 'Biological' ORDER BY process_id
SELECT tank_id, tank_size, water_type FROM aquaculture_tanks WHERE water_circulation_system_id IN (SELECT system_id FROM water_circulation_systems WHERE system_type = 'Recirculating')
SELECT tank_id, tank_size, water_type, oxygen_level FROM aquaculture_tanks JOIN oxygen_levels ON aquaculture_tanks.tank_id = oxygen_levels.tank_id WHERE oxygen_level > 5
SELECT * FROM WaterCirculationSystems;
SELECT system_name, pump_capacity FROM WaterCirculationSystems;
SELECT tank_name, tank_size FROM AquacultureTanks WHERE water_type = 'freshwater';
SELECT process_name, filter_type FROM FiltrationProcesses ORDER BY process_id DESC;
SELECT fish_species, quantity FROM FishStock WHERE quantity > 100 ORDER BY quantity DESC;
SELECT system_name, pump_capacity FROM WaterCirculationSystems;
SELECT tank_name, water_type, tank_size FROM AquacultureTanks ORDER BY tank_size DESC;
SELECT process_name, filter_capacity FROM FiltrationProcesses WHERE filter_type = 'Sand';
SELECT fish_species, quantity FROM FishStock WHERE quantity > 100 ORDER BY quantity DESC;
SELECT tank_name, tank_size, water_type FROM AquacultureTanks JOIN FishStock ON AquacultureTanks.tank_id = FishStock.tank_id WHERE FishStock.quantity > 50;
